ADDTEAM TeamA
ADDTEAM TeamB
ADDTEAM TeamC
START DURATION 100 PROBLEM 3
SUBMIT A BY TeamA WITH Accepted AT 10
SUBMIT B BY TeamB WITH Wrong_Answer AT 20
FLUSH
QUERY_RANKING TeamA
QUERY_RANKING TeamB
QUERY_RANKING TeamC
SUBMIT B BY TeamB WITH Accepted AT 30
FLUSH
QUERY_RANKING TeamA
QUERY_RANKING TeamB
FREEZE
SUBMIT C BY TeamA WITH Accepted AT 50
SCROLL
END
